name: Im Under The Rock
chorusText:
I’m under the Rock
and the Rock is higher than I
For Jesus hides me
I’m under the Rock

Go tell my enemies
That I am safe
for Jesus hides me
I’m under the Rock
Ek is onder Sy vlerk
en Sy vlerk is hoër as ek
want Jesus beskerm my
ek is onder Sy vlerk

gaan vertel my vyande
ek is vry
want Jesus beskerm my
ek is onder Sy vlerk
